  "content": ";\">Error messages lie.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;\">The GPU error pointed at memory. The real cause was the display server. Always read the logs.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- Takeaway 2 -->\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;\">🤝</div>\n      <div style=\"min-width: 0;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 8px;\">AI collaboration > AI answers.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;\">Claude got it wrong first. I steered us back. Neither would have solved it alone.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Takeaway 3 -->\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 28px 32px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;\">⚙️</div>\n      <div style=\"min-width: 0;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 8px;\">The engineering stack becomes the creative stack.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;\">Same Linux setup. Same hardware. Now running a full video editing workflow.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 16px 0;\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; padding: 8px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n      Anyone else using AI to streamline their video editing workflow?\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-muted);\">\n      Curious what people have landed on.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">07 / 07</div>\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
